Package: limmaVoomCLI
Title: limma-voom DE pipeline broken into 5 callable steps
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Anne", "Deslattes Mays", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "adeslat@scitechcon.org")
Description: Pseudobulk differential expression via limma-voom,
    structured as a 5-step pipeline. Each step is a pure R function in
    R/ and an Rscript entry in inst/scripts/. Each Rscript becomes a
    Nextflow module.
